Sentencas: Layered GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+delta(GBSCCu) perovskite oxide is synthesised using an ethylenediaminetetraacetic acid (EDTA)-citrate combined method.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical performances are investigated as a novel cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cathode GBSCCu chemical compatibility with Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (GDC) electrolyte is examined below 950 degrees C.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity value of the GBSCCu sample reaches a maximum of 147 Scm(-1) at 750 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient of the GBSCCu sample is 16.9 x 10(-6) K-1 between 30 degrees C and 900 degrees C.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The polarisation resistance of GBSCCu on the GDC electrolyte is 0.102 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density of a single cell with a GBSCCu-GDC composite cathode on the 300 mu m thick GDC electrolyte reaches 402 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results indicate that GBSCCu is a potential cathode material for GDC electrolyte intermediate-temperaturte solid oxide fuel cells(IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBa0.5Sr0.5CoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
